{"tid":96322,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[師傅請進] 我隻手越來越多掌紋","createTime":"2017-01-26T17:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T10:26:10.000Z","uid":11805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18c506784838f2c57e575901eecf4c8038884ada","tid":96322,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隻手由細開始已經好多掌紋<br />\n但近排望望下<br />\n發現左啲新生既淺幼紋<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問 隻手咁撚多紋點記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但日日望住多左幾條總會覺得有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道人既掌紋會隨年日而變<br />\n有無師傅解釋下會有咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申未到三十<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/27/013602_f587c701548b581f9afd946c56708ca1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F27%2F013602_f587c701548b581f9afd946c56708ca1.jpg&h=1f8f6438&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d216ea90e9646e08017648817db4004c9329480b","tid":96322,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:45:23.000Z","msg":"奇才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6c44a6155c5064f8ccbf977cd6b1723b144aff","tid":96322,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:47:28.000Z","msg":"會陽萎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好打咁多j喇"},{"pid":"fbb4cac21a8e7cc18df8d4179af58cf714c292da","tid":96322,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"你女朋友咁樣衰既"},{"pid":"2e8416f0d51196f1a0fdfcde112ef9feac0fac85","tid":96322,"uid":57985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"我啲掌紋仲深仲多 愈黎愈多 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/no